outputs.output_descr:
The project entails budgetary allocation to Resident Coordination Office, Suva for coordination results purposes. There are three core result areas of the mentioned project: coordination for results, Coordination of Emergency Preparedness and Relief, UN Advocacy and Resource Mobilization, Security Management, and Non-Resident UN Agencies.

Coordination for Results - a) UNDAF Rollout exercise undertaken in 2011 b) Review of Joint Presence Office, Joint Programmes and Kiribati One Fund c) National & Regional MDG/BPOA Reports produced and disseminated in preparations for the UN Global Summits t
